title: BackTrack 5 R3 GNOME 32Bit VM
description:
BackTrack is a Linux-based penetration testing arsenal that aids security professionals in the ability to perform assessments in a purely native environment dedicated to hacking.
Lastest version of backtrack 5 R3

This is the version that is to be ran by a virtual machine. I personally recommend VMware or virtual Box.

After you install your virtual machine application of yo7ur choose. Just extract file and double click on the file called BT5R3-GNOME-VM-32.vmx and you're all set.
